{"tid":228241,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"騎牛等馬 好撚過份？","createTime":"2017-05-03T17:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T19:04:15.000Z","uid":90520,"like":6,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"638ecc25e7087f71f27523d68c53e57b4fc30885","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:48:55.000Z","msg":"有一個女仔 我鍾意咗佢3年<br />\n明戀 暗戀 都試過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢亦都知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我估<br />\n<br />\n最初 我想追佢 <br />\n不過佢突然有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我拍住拖等<br />\n<br />\n然後我分手 佢未分<br />\n<br />\n到佢分手 我又有拖<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎 都仍然好鍾意個女仔<br />\n就算同人拍拖 都仍然將佢擺放係心入面<br />\n你當現任7分 佢3分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拍拖嗰陣一直都冇做一啲對唔住對方嘅事<br />\n所以 其實我真係冇乜愧疚咁<br />\n<br />\n不過最近同個朋友提起<br />\n佢話我咁樣好撚賤 根本係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屬於精神出軌之類咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人之常情 無錯到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">話說講開 我兩次都係比人飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"daa688a1063937acedb99e871488cf37d481094c","tid":228241,"uid":114062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"同你拍過拖果d好慘"},{"pid":"faa8e67c9f01e7de942ae42ee5a9d66c81e3c47a","tid":228241,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:52:40.000Z","msg":"冇心就咪撚搞人啦"},{"pid":"3b4c895510643cf534269f753cc4c6d9ff72f5ac","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你拍過拖果d好慘</blockquote><br />\n其實勁擺心機落去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過 收埋咗另一個女人係心咁"},{"pid":"780ad2339f81d8ce39bcdefefb08c0d86ad70119","tid":228241,"uid":114062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你拍過拖果d好慘</blockquote><br />\n其實勁擺心機落去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過 收埋咗另一個女人係心咁</blockquote><br />\n講多無謂 唔好整多個受害者出來"},{"pid":"06286d420ee2c991c7bdd538ddc972e611815d9e","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇心就咪撚搞人啦</blockquote><br />\n拍咗三次<br />\n一次雞<br />\n一次勁難忘 不過知道對方唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近嗰次 直頭係好似得到女神咁<br />\n不過直頭唔啱key<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 每一次都投放哂全副心機<br />\n不過 對方 唔係自己所想嘅一個咁"},{"pid":"f232db9a2cfd3df8055e97dc9a1c61cf542e9d21","tid":228241,"uid":114062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇心就咪撚搞人啦</blockquote><br />\n拍咗三次<br />\n一次雞<br />\n一次勁難忘 不過知道對方唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近嗰次 直頭係好似得到女神咁<br />\n不過直頭唔啱key<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 每一次都投放哂全副心機<br />\n不過 對方 唔係自己所想嘅一個咁</blockquote><br />\n個心仲有另一個都叫全副心機"},{"pid":"469eaf89f055b98fe0dfedb144053fbed9c2fd62","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你拍過拖果d好慘</blockquote><br />\n其實勁擺心機落去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過 收埋咗另一個女人係心咁</blockquote><br />\n講多無謂 唔好整多個受害者出來</blockquote><br />\n其實 我對佢地每個都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932990bef9c967d079fdefd00eb889214d30f9db","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇心就咪撚搞人啦</blockquote><br />\n拍咗三次<br />\n一次雞<br />\n一次勁難忘 不過知道對方唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近嗰次 直頭係好似得到女神咁<br />\n不過直頭唔啱key<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 每一次都投放哂全副心機<br />\n不過 對方 唔係自己所想嘅一個咁</blockquote><br />\n個心仲有另一個都叫全副心機</blockquote><br />\n另一個女人 可能係夢想 可能係妄想<br />\n對住現任 我已經將我比到嘅比佢"},{"pid":"4d2b0d142c088dc1dce3291c918db948a2148e7b","tid":228241,"uid":104820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:03:32.000Z","msg":"你咪撚再害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba88f7ef87803bb12182b664cae30c8ef0d2b760","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪撚再害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多啲？<br />\n問心 我完全冇對佢地差過<br />\n分咗手 佢地都話我唔應該對佢咁好之類<br />\n<br />\n所以 其實邊到有問題<br />\n想知"},{"pid":"197b53981f2250a4b08cc2f706eca05c469a9f2d","tid":228241,"uid":114062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇心就咪撚搞人啦</blockquote><br />\n拍咗三次<br />\n一次雞<br />\n一次勁難忘 不過知道對方唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近嗰次 直頭係好似得到女神咁<br />\n不過直頭唔啱key<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 每一次都投放哂全副心機<br />\n不過 對方 唔係自己所想嘅一個咁</blockquote><br />\n個心仲有另一個都叫全副心機</blockquote><br />\n另一個女人 可能係夢想 可能係妄想<br />\n對住現任 我已經將我比到嘅比佢</blockquote><br />\n咁你講到咁 可能唔係你問題<br />\n但你同人拍緊拖 個心仲有另一個<br />\n有點無言"},{"pid":"c22f1f53ce9763d05d3f6011396cc2aa22282fc4","tid":228241,"uid":104820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你咪撚再害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多啲？<br />\n問心 我完全冇對佢地差過<br />\n分咗手 佢地都話我唔應該對佢咁好之類<br />\n<br />\n所以 其實邊到有問題<br />\n想知</blockquote><br />\n你都仲識問 未衰得晒 唔好跳住 落返黎先<br />\n問題就係對一個人應該係一心一意 即使你認為冇問題 對方都唔覺得有問題 但你個心有第二個就係唔ok<br />\n同邊個 就係全心全意對佢 唔會諗其他人"},{"pid":"9098e2a32ec1a77af03df477b948e920ae9716f8","tid":228241,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"我都試過拍緊拖，但係心入面一直都有另一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個完美符合自己夢中情人形象嘅人。<br />\n但係唔會因為佢而同自己一齊緊嘅女仔分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為咁樣實在太賤"},{"pid":"11b00cb816a9a62c4c02fb75f4a7c189a532cbd2","tid":228241,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3113e94251a2603ca13daec25f92542c8111af74","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇心就咪撚搞人啦</blockquote><br />\n拍咗三次<br />\n一次雞<br />\n一次勁難忘 不過知道對方唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近嗰次 直頭係好似得到女神咁<br />\n不過直頭唔啱key<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 每一次都投放哂全副心機<br />\n不過 對方 唔係自己所想嘅一個咁</blockquote><br />\n個心仲有另一個都叫全副心機</blockquote><br />\n另一個女人 可能係夢想 可能係妄想<br />\n對住現任 我已經將我比到嘅比佢</blockquote><br />\n咁你講到咁 可能唔係你問題<br />\n但你同人拍緊拖 個心仲有另一個<br />\n有點無言</blockquote><br />\n呢個人於我而言真係好特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實凡係男人 應該都感受過<br />\n我愛的人 不是我的愛人<br />\n眼睛張開身邊竟是誰<br />\n歌都有得唱<br />\n<br />\n現任係水泡？係安全島？<br />\n可能係<br />\n<br />\n不過我至少對佢地係盡責<br />\n因為我知道 身為男朋友 <br />\n有乜做得 有乜唔做得<br />\n<br />\n我亦都冇因爲個 另一個 而放棄現任"},{"pid":"d2f2662700afb3bc7f9b523f5cdaf626369ffe04","tid":228241,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"巴打，我明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實可能因為未同過對方拍拖，所以會對佢有好大幻想，覺得同佢一定咩都夾得黎。用自己嘅幻想比較現任，現任當然點都無咁好。<br />\n<br />\n巴打你有呢個心態係正常，況且你都應該同呢個心底裏嘅女仔識咗一段時間，所以幻想得多日久生情都唔出奇。因為我都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但盡可能都同自己講要對現任負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. A3"},{"pid":"8d9e323216b35adae121c7529c2d06fcaca0b3b4","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過拍緊拖，但係心入面一直都有另一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個完美符合自己夢中情人形象嘅人。<br />\n但係唔會因為佢而同自己一齊緊嘅女仔分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為咁樣實在太賤</blockquote><br />\nExact7ly 終於有同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7243d2d604ff148a7795f617c2dc2d31802800ab","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你咪撚再害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多啲？<br />\n問心 我完全冇對佢地差過<br />\n分咗手 佢地都話我唔應該對佢咁好之類<br />\n<br />\n所以 其實邊到有問題<br />\n想知</blockquote><br />\n你都仲識問 未衰得晒 唔好跳住 落返黎先<br />\n問題就係對一個人應該係一心一意 即使你認為冇問題 對方都唔覺得有問題 但你個心有第二個就係唔ok<br />\n同邊個 就係全心全意對佢 唔會諗其他人</blockquote><br />\n係 我都覺得係<br />\n細細個 無論睇漫畫 小說乜都好<br />\n男朋友對女朋友 應該都要全心全意<br />\n<br />\n不過現實 人係經唔撚起寂莫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗 大概就係我賤嘅主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758fcec8b6d7f34179b74a70b5c20ae0852ec68b","tid":228241,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，我明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實可能因為未同過對方拍拖，所以會對佢有好大幻想，覺得同佢一定咩都夾得黎。用自己嘅幻想比較現任，現任當然點都無咁好。<br />\n<br />\n巴打你有呢個心態係正常，況且你都應該同呢個心底裏嘅女仔識咗一段時間，所以幻想得多日久生情都唔出奇。因為我都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但盡可能都同自己講要對現任負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. A3</blockquote><br />\n夾？可能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都可能唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係知道 我鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為佢 我好多野都變咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包括性格 興趣<br />\n至少 由當初嘅大毒撚 變成今日嘅半social 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928ce57b8abd893f65949b1c19d492d7151e16e7","tid":228241,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都試過拍緊拖，但係心入面一直都有另一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個完美符合自己夢中情人形象嘅人。<br />\n但係唔會因為佢而同自己一齊緊嘅女仔分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為咁樣實在太賤</blockquote><br />\nExact7ly 終於有同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過比女朋友問，點解咁鍾意女神又同佢一齊?好直接咁答佢，因為女神唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6052d1d153417003eae5b