oji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有一個心底好鍾意嘅人，雖然見到無見過面。識咗好多年傾咗好長時間，而且佢嘅條件都好好，但佢唔係香港人，隔咗個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果要維持就一定要long d仲要唔知幾時先可以面對面咁長時間相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca89bad70c36de58f97a7b938c5c328bbf37e37","tid":228241,"uid":96979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你拍過拖果d好慘</blockquote><br />\n其實勁擺心機落去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過 收埋咗另一個女人係心咁</blockquote><br />\n我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係三年<br />\n而且我當左人水泡咁<br />\n不過依加冇了<br />\n放低左"}]}